---
import Layout from "../layouts/BlogPost.astro";
import { PHONE, PHONE_HREF, LICENSE_NUMBER, PROVIDER_FIRST_NAME } from "../consts";
---

<Layout
	title="About J&K Daycare | Licensed Family Child Care in Springfield, MA"
	description="Meet Magaly, the licensed provider behind J&K Daycare — a small, home-based family child care for children ages 2–6 in East Forest Park, Springfield, MA."
	pubDate={new Date("June 1, 2026")}
	heroImage="/about.jpg"
>
	<p>
		J&amp;K Daycare is a small, licensed <strong>family child care</strong> in the East Forest Park
		neighborhood of Springfield, MA. We care for a small group of up to six children ages 2–6 in a
		warm home setting — so every child gets real attention, consistent routines, and a place that
		feels like a second home.
	</p>

	<p>
		Hi, I'm <strong>{PROVIDER_FIRST_NAME}</strong>, the licensed provider. Our days are play-based
		and gently structured: sensory and hands-on play, early literacy and math, music and movement,
		outdoor time, and nutritious meals and snacks included every day. Our staff are CPR &amp;
		First-Aid certified, and we're licensed by the Massachusetts Department of Early Education &amp;
		Care (EEC), license #{LICENSE_NUMBER}.
	</p>

	<p>
		We'd love to meet your family. Call <a href={PHONE_HREF}>{PHONE}</a> to schedule a tour, or
		<a href="/#tour">request a tour online</a> and we'll follow up with details and current
		availability.
	</p>
</Layout>
